---
import GlobalLayout from '../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro';
import TeamGrid from '../components/TeamGrid.astro';
---

<GlobalLayout title="About Us | Our Mission | Infinite Wealth Academy" description="Our mission: protecting 500 families by 2027. Education first, strategic protection, and sustainable long-term strategies. Partner with Infinite Wealth Academy.">
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 lg:py-28 border-b border-amber-500/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
        Protecting Families. Strengthening Futures.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Infinite Wealth Academy exists to help families gain financial clarity, strengthen protection, and build long-term confidence through education and strategic planning.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-0">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Our Mission: Protecting 500 Families by 2027</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Where Financial Clarity Meets Family Security. Infinite Wealth Academy helps families build strong financial foundations through education, protection planning, and sustainable long-term strategies.
          </p>
          <a href="/book" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-bold rounded-md text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-amber-600 hover:from-yellow-400 hover:to-amber-500 transition-all shadow-md">
            Partner With Us
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Education First</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Empowering families to understand exactly how money works before making decisions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-amber-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Strategic Protection</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Moving beyond saving to ensure your assets and income are properly shielded.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2 border-l-4 border-amber-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Sustainable Long-Term Strategies</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Designing flexible retirement and generational wealth plans that adapt to life's inevitable changes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl hidden lg:block">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/case-study-advisor.png" alt="Advisor consulting with a couple over a laptop" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4">Real Impact</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10">
            How One Family Gained More Control Over Their Financial Future.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-4 top-8 bg-slate-900 text-amber-400 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow-md">1</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Their Concern</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                They felt uncertainty about market volatility and were unsure if their current savings plan provided enough protection against unforeseen life events or the retirement income gap.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-4 top-8 bg-slate-900 text-amber-400 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow-md">2</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What They Discovered</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                Through our customized Financial Needs Analysis, they realized traditional advice had overlooked living benefits, income protection, and tax-advantaged strategies.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-4 top-8 bg-slate-900 text-amber-400 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow-md">3</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">The Result</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                By repositioning their assets, they achieved immediate financial clarity, improved flexibility for retirement income, and established generational confidence.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TeamGrid />
</GlobalLayout>
